03:45.392 --> 03:47.059
( grunts )

03:50.396 --> 03:54.199
Okay, Magic Instruction Book,
instruct me.

03:54.201 --> 03:56.835
Oh, no,
Glossaryck is frozen too.

03:56.837 --> 03:59.037
Good.
I never liked that guy.

03:59.039 --> 04:01.540
Scrape the sides, buddy.

04:01.542 --> 04:03.041
Okay, let's see, let's see.

04:03.043 --> 04:04.776
What to do if you make
a dimension explode.

04:04.778 --> 04:06.845
What to do
if you delete gravity.

04:06.847 --> 04:09.047
<i>Oh.</i>
<i>Don't get any ideas.</i>

04:09.049 --> 04:10.315
Heh-heh. Sorry.

04:10.317 --> 04:13.051
Ah!
What to do if you freeze time.

04:13.053 --> 04:16.788
We can move time forward
if we go to the planes of time

04:16.790 --> 04:19.124
and push the wheel
of progress.

04:22.262 --> 04:23.762
Whoa.

04:23.764 --> 04:25.831
This is definitely

04:25.833 --> 04:27.899
one of the weirder places
we've been to.

04:27.901 --> 04:31.970
Weirder than that dimension
of cats with human faces?

04:31.972 --> 04:33.538
Here, kitty, kitty!

04:33.540 --> 04:36.908
(demonic voice)
Look away!

04:36.910 --> 04:37.809
( shivering )

04:37.811 --> 04:39.211
Look!

04:39.213 --> 04:41.146
That must be it.

04:41.148 --> 04:42.914
Whoa.

04:42.916 --> 04:44.983
Looks like
a giant hamster wheel.

04:44.985 --> 04:48.086
STAR: Now,
how do we start this thing?

04:48.088 --> 04:50.322
Hmm. I got this.

04:52.191 --> 04:54.960
( grunting )

05:01.034 --> 05:04.503
New plan.
Rainbow Raccoon Rotation.

05:07.340 --> 05:08.440
Hmm.

05:08.442 --> 05:10.375
Magic won't work on that.

05:10.377 --> 05:13.078
You got to use
the magic of toesies.

05:14.814 --> 05:16.148
Who are you?

05:16.150 --> 05:19.985
I'm Father Time.
And this is Rocksworth.

05:19.987 --> 05:21.987
He's  a rock,
but don't bring it up,

05:21.989 --> 05:23.989
he's kind of sensitive
about it.

05:23.991 --> 05:25.257
( makes motorboat sounds )

05:25.259 --> 05:28.860
Father Time?
So you must push this thing.

05:29.996 --> 05:32.030
Hey, look!
I'm over here.

05:32.032 --> 05:35.500
And now, I'm over here!
Ha ha ha ha!

05:35.502 --> 05:38.970
And how long
were you  <i>on </i> the wheel?

05:38.972 --> 05:41.139
Oh, you know, forever.

05:41.141 --> 05:42.941
Until someone
cast a freeze spell

05:42.943 --> 05:44.209
and knocked me off of it.

05:44.211 --> 05:46.378
What is  <i>that?</i>

05:46.380 --> 05:48.246
Uh, mud?

05:49.182 --> 05:51.516
Oh, it's glorious!

05:51.518 --> 05:53.452
