05:55.388 --> 05:56.521
( gags )

05:57.957 --> 06:00.559
So, Mr. Time,
how would you feel about

06:00.561 --> 06:02.594
getting the universe
started up again?

06:02.596 --> 06:06.365
Oh, where has this been
all of my life?

06:06.367 --> 06:07.966
Ah, look, look, look.

06:07.968 --> 06:10.902
You can play with mud
on your wheel.

06:10.904 --> 06:12.204
Huh?
Huh?

06:12.206 --> 06:16.541
Well, that is an enticing offer,
but nah.

06:16.543 --> 06:19.344
Arrghh!
Oh! There's some mud
that's a slightly
different color.

06:19.346 --> 06:21.346
And there's a twig,
and there's a bush,

06:21.348 --> 06:24.416
and I don't know
what that thing is,
but it's waddling.

06:24.418 --> 06:26.952
Wait! You can't just
leave time stopped!

06:26.954 --> 06:28.887
Whoo!

06:28.889 --> 06:30.322
But without time,

06:30.324 --> 06:32.090
rainbows can't shoot
across the sky,

06:32.092 --> 06:33.925
glitter can't glitter!

06:33.927 --> 06:36.061
And everyone we know
will be frozen forever!

06:36.063 --> 06:38.363
What's this?

06:38.365 --> 06:39.998
Ooh!

06:40.933 --> 06:42.033
( laughing )

06:42.035 --> 06:44.536
YOLO! Ha ha!

06:44.538 --> 06:46.171
Anything's possible.

06:49.575 --> 06:51.910
Yah! Whoo-hoo!

06:51.912 --> 06:54.946
( clock ticking )

06:54.948 --> 06:57.082
I hate this dimension.

06:57.084 --> 06:59.451
Ha ha ha! Whoo!

06:59.453 --> 07:01.753
Oh! Ha ha ha ha!

07:09.095 --> 07:12.297
Oh, my hearts.

07:16.002 --> 07:17.436
Not a word.

07:17.438 --> 07:18.537
Hee hee hee!

07:22.008 --> 07:23.141
I think he went in there.

07:25.945 --> 07:27.579
Wow.

07:27.581 --> 07:30.248
It's the history
of the whole universe.

07:30.250 --> 07:33.218
Ooh! Battle of Lexington.
Nailed it.

07:43.095 --> 07:44.563
( gasps ) It--

07:44.565 --> 07:45.964
It's me!

07:52.305 --> 07:54.372
Oh, I remember that!

07:56.108 --> 07:59.211
( chuckling )
Watching me is fun.

08:01.481 --> 08:03.782
Oh!
Hi, me!

08:03.784 --> 08:06.751
This place must keep track
of everything we've done
in our lives.

08:32.178 --> 08:37.015
Wow. I've been nodding
for a long time.

08:37.017 --> 08:38.250
FATHER TIME: Hey, guys!

08:38.252 --> 08:41.186
Isn't this place incredible?

08:41.188 --> 08:43.088
It's like we're living
in the future.

08:43.090 --> 08:44.122
Father Time!

08:44.124 --> 08:46.024
Emerald Snake Strike!

08:48.060 --> 08:49.694
Great.
I think we got him.

08:50.730 --> 08:52.497
Yuck. Okay, buddy,

08:52.499 --> 08:54.299
let's get you
back to your wheel.

08:54.301 --> 08:55.634
( gasps )

09:09.282 --> 09:12.584
( clock ticking )

09:12.586 --> 09:15.186
Ahh, all right.

09:15.188 --> 09:17.122
I guess I'll get back
to doing that.

09:17.124 --> 09:19.758
Oh, well,
it's only for all eternity.

09:19.760 --> 09:21.359
( sighs )

09:21.361 --> 09:23.061
