to turn that giant wheel.

09:26.233 --> 09:29.234
( chittering )

09:29.236 --> 09:32.470
Are you thinkin'
what I'm thinkin'?

09:32.472 --> 09:36.474
Actually, I was thinking we'd--
Never mind, it works.

09:36.476 --> 09:38.743
Now you can go
anywhere you want,

09:38.745 --> 09:40.245
<i>and </i> keep the wheel moving!

09:40.247 --> 09:43.181
Aww, thanks, guys.
I owe ya.

09:43.183 --> 09:44.816
Please, help yourself
to any of my mud.

09:44.818 --> 09:47.285
Even the nice stuff.
We're good.

09:47.287 --> 09:49.588
Oh, and maybe
don't freeze time again.

09:49.590 --> 09:52.223
It's kind of fragile.
You don't want to break it.

09:52.225 --> 09:53.258
Know what I mean?

09:53.260 --> 09:55.260
Well, so long. Ha ha!

09:55.262 --> 09:58.597
Time hamsters away!
Yoo-hoo!

10:02.768 --> 10:04.402
