We've got to get back!

10:06.106 --> 10:07.439
( clock ticking )

10:09.275 --> 10:10.475
( puppies yipping )

10:10.477 --> 10:11.843
( singing )

10:13.145 --> 10:14.879
Whoa!
Aaaah!

10:25.625 --> 10:27.192
Hey, Jackie.

10:28.728 --> 10:30.161
Hey, Marco.

10:31.397 --> 10:33.331
Well, see ya.

10:36.636 --> 10:39.437
You did it!
You finally talked to her!

10:39.439 --> 10:41.439
What happened
to waiting for the perfect time?

10:41.441 --> 10:43.274
Well, all of a sudden,
I thought,

10:43.276 --> 10:45.777
if you have the time,
why waste it?

10:45.779 --> 10:47.746
Looks like I'm finally

10:47.748 --> 10:50.281
( slow-mo )
getting somewhere...

10:50.283 --> 10:53.718
Ha ha! You guys really get me!

10:57.223 --> 10:58.256
( yawning )

10:58.258 --> 11:00.925
STAR: Morning, Marco!
Hey.

11:00.927 --> 11:04.162
Aaaah! Whoaah!

11:04.164 --> 11:06.931
( Marco screaming )

11:06.933 --> 11:10.368
( laughing ) Whooo!

11:10.370 --> 11:11.803
Oh, that was awesome!

11:11.805 --> 11:13.505
I know, right?

11:13.507 --> 11:16.474
Stairs are so boring.

11:16.476 --> 11:18.810
I hope my parents don't flip
when they see this.

11:18.812 --> 11:20.278
MAN: I'm flipping!

11:21.647 --> 11:24.516
Dad!
Relax, son.

11:24.518 --> 11:28.453
