13:02.783 --> 13:05.683
Whoo-hoo-hoo-hoo!

13:05.685 --> 13:08.720
( creatures giggling )

13:09.822 --> 13:11.456
Get him!
Get him!

13:11.458 --> 13:12.423
Gut him like a fish!

13:12.425 --> 13:14.926
I got 20 bucks on Teddy!

13:14.928 --> 13:16.327
ALL: Hi, Star!

13:16.329 --> 13:17.829
I'm Kevin.
I'm new.

13:17.831 --> 13:20.298
Magnificent!

13:20.300 --> 13:22.333
If you like this,
let me show you

13:22.335 --> 13:24.803
the most magical room
in the whole house.

13:24.805 --> 13:27.472
The bathroom!

13:27.474 --> 13:30.909
( gasping, grunting )

13:30.911 --> 13:32.744
What a glorious throne!

13:32.746 --> 13:35.480
Why does it have a hole?

13:35.482 --> 13:40.351
Um, humans put things in there
and flush 'em down.

13:40.353 --> 13:42.053
Flush?
What's a flush?

13:43.489 --> 13:44.622
( water flushing )

13:44.624 --> 13:47.959
My word,
where does the water go?

13:47.961 --> 13:50.361
Nobody knows.

13:50.363 --> 13:54.465
It's one of Earth's
greatest mysteries.

13:54.467 --> 13:56.434
Does this go in it?

13:56.436 --> 13:57.969
All the time.

13:58.904 --> 14:00.405
( flushing )

14:02.741 --> 14:04.809
( gasps )

14:04.811 --> 14:09.047
( huffing, puffing )

14:09.049 --> 14:11.683
This?
I don't see why not.

14:11.685 --> 14:13.918
(flushing )

14:13.920 --> 14:14.919
This?

14:14.921 --> 14:16.821
Go for it.

14:16.823 --> 14:19.524
DAD: This?
STAR: Go ahead!

14:19.526 --> 14:20.992
What are they doing in there?

14:20.994 --> 14:22.861
( laughing )
This?

14:22.863 --> 14:25.430
Do it.

14:25.432 --> 14:27.465
( flushing )

14:27.467 --> 14:29.067
( growling )

14:31.036 --> 14:32.070
Hey, Marco.

14:32.072 --> 14:33.838
DAD: Love the bathroom!

14:33.840 --> 14:36.841
Thanks. What's next
on the itinerary for the d--

14:36.843 --> 14:39.377
Ohh-ohh-ohhhh!

14:39.379 --> 14:40.879
