this tiny moon into that hole.

14:46.686 --> 14:49.454
Ha ha!
What fun!

14:49.456 --> 14:52.457
You're holding your club
upside-down.

14:52.459 --> 14:54.025
This is a club?

14:54.027 --> 14:56.628
There's one thing
we got better on Mewni.

14:56.630 --> 14:58.630
Tally-ho!

15:00.699 --> 15:03.468
Ha ha! How's that for
getting it into the hole?

15:04.603 --> 15:06.404
What's that?

15:06.406 --> 15:07.805
♪ ( music box )

15:07.807 --> 15:10.074
That's the Candy Castle.
The next hole.

15:10.076 --> 15:12.977
Lord Salivary
of the Weebler elf clan.

15:12.979 --> 15:14.946
You sly dog!

15:14.948 --> 15:17.482
( roars )
What?

15:17.484 --> 15:19.517
Ha ha!

15:19.519 --> 15:22.487
Mommy,
why is Santa doing that?

15:22.489 --> 15:24.055
Dad!

15:24.057 --> 15:27.425
I'll teach you to give my wife
the googly eye!

15:27.427 --> 15:28.960
Dad, stop it!

15:31.430 --> 15:34.599
( people screaming )
DAD: Ha ha!

15:34.601 --> 15:37.702
The ball's in your court,
Salivary!

15:43.042 --> 15:45.443
( moaning )

15:45.445 --> 15:46.544
( sniffing )

15:48.647 --> 15:51.082
( screaming )

15:51.084 --> 15:54.552
