Dad, what are you doing?

16:06.199 --> 16:08.466
Ha ha ha! Hello, darling!

16:09.501 --> 16:11.569
It's the middle of the night.

16:11.571 --> 16:14.105
Ah, the perfect time
for a tussle.

16:14.107 --> 16:16.474
Isn't that right, clowney?

16:16.476 --> 16:18.042
The name is Kevin,
old man!

16:18.044 --> 16:20.478
Arrr!

16:20.480 --> 16:22.146
Give it up, clown!

16:22.148 --> 16:23.614
Bring the pain!

16:25.718 --> 16:27.785
I can do this all night.

16:27.787 --> 16:29.721
DAD: Ha ha ha!
CLOWN: Chicky-wink.

16:34.493 --> 16:35.693
Good morning, Star.

16:35.695 --> 16:37.729
Ba-ba-ba-ba-ba-ba.

16:39.498 --> 16:42.633
It was ridiculously loud
last night.

16:42.635 --> 16:45.169
It wasn't me, Oscar.
It was my dad.

16:45.171 --> 16:46.771
He's insane!

16:46.773 --> 16:48.539
He just thinks
he can come down to Earth

16:48.541 --> 16:49.607
and do whatever he wants.

16:49.609 --> 16:51.576
He is so inconsiderate.

16:51.578 --> 16:54.645
Huh.
I can weirdly relate.

16:54.647 --> 16:55.680
What do you mean?

16:55.682 --> 16:58.182
Doesn't that sound  <i>familiar?</i>

17:00.119 --> 17:02.253
Yeah.

17:02.255 --> 17:05.089
He does this to my mom.

17:05.091 --> 17:07.725
Never mind.

17:07.727 --> 17:10.828
Well, I'm just glad
he's leaving today.

17:10.830 --> 17:13.531
I don't know how much
more of this I can take.

17:13.533 --> 17:15.600
Hello, Star.

17:15.602 --> 17:18.069
Dad, what are you doing?

17:18.071 --> 17:19.937
I'm hanging lights
for the party.

17:19.939 --> 17:22.540
What party?
Oh, jeez!

17:22.542 --> 17:24.042
I forgot to tell you.

17:24.044 --> 17:26.277
I'm having
such a great time here,

17:26.279 --> 17:28.579
I've decided to stay.

17:28.581 --> 17:29.647
Isn't that great?

17:29.649 --> 17:31.582
Greeeeeat.

17:31.584 --> 17:33.651
Oh, and in celebration
of moving here,

17:33.653 --> 17:36.587
I've invited some friends
to check out my new digs.

17:36.589 --> 17:37.822
( doorbell ringing )
They're here.

17:37.824 --> 17:40.558
( party chatter )

17:40.560 --> 17:42.260
Chew, chew, chew,
chew, chew!

17:42.262 --> 17:45.630
( giggling )
Don't wake him up, man.

17:45.632 --> 17:48.099
We'll see if Salivary
recovers from this one.

17:48.101 --> 17:50.001
( laughing )

17:50.003 --> 17:52.070
Dad, I really need
to talk to you right now.

17:52.072 --> 17:53.604
HELIOS: Hey, guys!

17:53.606 --> 17:57.008
Well, here I am! Yeah!
Now the party can start.

17:57.010 --> 17:59.077
Ha ha! Ooh, tight squeeze.

18:00.045 --> 18:01.345
My bad.

18:01.347 --> 18:04.415
Oh, no.
Who invited Helios?

18:04.417 --> 18:06.651
That guy is the worst.

18:06.653 --> 18:09.754
Gross!
Now he got his ear pierced?

18:09.756 --> 18:13.224
There he goes,
eating all the appetizers.

18:13.226 --> 18:14.659
He ruins every party

18:14.661 --> 18:16.894
and is completely
oblivious about it.

18:16.896 --> 18:19.697
Funny.
I can weirdly relate.

18:19.699 --> 18:22.934
Look, people are already
going into orbit around him.

18:22.936 --> 18:24.902
No, no, no! Please, somebody!

18:24.904 --> 18:26.737
His gravitational pull--

18:26.739 --> 18:28.906
So why don't you
just kick him out?

18:28.908 --> 18:31.275
Along with  <i>everyone </i> else?

18:31.277 --> 18:33.911
No way.
I'm not talking to that tool.

18:33.913 --> 18:35.046
Ugh!

18:36.081 --> 18:37.248
Uh, hey, guys.

18:37.250 --> 18:38.850
Are those water balloo--
Whoa!

18:38.852 --> 18:40.651
Punch. Punch. Punch.

18:40.653 --> 18:43.054
No, no, no, no, no.
Whoah!

18:43.056 --> 18:46.290
Your feet are so soft.

18:46.292 --> 18:48.659
Aaaah! No!

18:48.661 --> 18:52.063
Whoo! Everybody, dancing really
sure works up my appe--

18:52.065 --> 18:53.397
Oho, dessert!

18:55.667 --> 18:57.935
Excuse me, I think
you've overstayed your welcome

18:57.937 --> 18:59.670
and you gotta go.

18:59.672 --> 19:02.874
Well,
you want to know something?

19:02.876 --> 19:04.408
I may be filled with hydrogen,

19:04.410 --> 19:06.344
but you're filled
with annoy-ogen.

19:06.346 --> 19:08.713
You just got
burned by the sun!

19:08.715 --> 19:10.047
( laughing )

19:10.049 --> 19:11.682
Whoa!

19:11.684 --> 19:13.217
MARCO:
I don't ask for much.

19:13.219 --> 19:16.354
Just a pair of dry socks,
that's all.

19:16.356 --> 19:19.290
It's like I'm mushing bananas
between my toes.

19:19.292 --> 19:21.659
Marco, I am so sorry

19:21.661 --> 19:23.661
that every time
I tried to have some fun,

19:23.663 --> 19:26.130
I ended up soaking your socks.

19:26.132 --> 19:28.766
Look, I love all the fun things
you want to do,

19:28.768 --> 19:31.235
just a little heads-up
would be nice.

19:31.237 --> 19:34.071
There's really nothing worse
than wet socks.

19:34.073 --> 19:36.374
Oh, yeah.

19:36.376 --> 19:38.309
Oh, yeah!

19:38.311 --> 19:40.978
Nothing worse than wet socks.

19:40.980 --> 19:42.847
( laughing )

19:42.849 --> 19:46.751
I'm still hungry,
but there's no more food.

19:46.753 --> 19:50.688
I guess I'll just have to eat
the whole planet!

19:50.690 --> 19:52.290
( gasp )

19:52.292 --> 19:54.859
It's time to purge this party.

19:56.228 --> 19:58.296
( groaning )

19:58.298 --> 20:01.032
Hey,  <i>two </i> pairs
of wet socks!

20:01.034 --> 20:02.800
I'm outta here.

20:05.237 --> 20:07.371
Because
I'm ridiculously apathetic

20:07.373 --> 20:10.041
to the suffering of others,
I'm leaving too.

20:10.043 --> 20:12.743
Gentlemen, gentlemen!

20:12.745 --> 20:14.779
Wow.

20:14.781 --> 20:17.081
I really made
a mess of things.

20:19.418 --> 20:22.753
There's no way
I'm poopin' out on  <i>this </i> party.

20:22.755 --> 20:24.121
Ahchoo!

20:24.123 --> 20:26.724
Um, sweetheart,

20:26.726 --> 20:29.994
I perhaps
got a little carried away.

20:29.996 --> 20:32.964
And I may have been
a little inconsiderate.

20:32.966 --> 20:37.235
I guess that's why your mother
threw me out in the first place.

20:37.237 --> 20:39.070
I'm sorry, you guys.

20:39.072 --> 20:41.372
And you'll patch
things up with Mom?

20:41.374 --> 20:42.907
Definitely.

20:42.909 --> 20:44.175
Hugs!
Hugs!

20:44.177 --> 20:45.910
What are you gonna do
with Helios?

20:45.912 --> 20:48.980
Ooh, after party!
Where we gonna go?

20:48.982 --> 20:52.917
I have no idea, but I'll
give you a ride! Ha ha!

20:52.919 --> 20:55.419
Tally-ho!
( Helios screaming )

20:55.421 --> 20:57.989
Hole in one! Ha ha ha ha!

20:57.991 --> 20:59.991
I'll send my top serfs here

20:59.993 --> 21:02.526
to make everything
better than new.

21:02.528 --> 21:03.594
Farewell.

21:03.596 --> 21:05.796
Bye, Dad.
Bye.

21:05.798 --> 21:08.466
Whew. From now on, I'll always
give you a heads-up.

21:08.468 --> 21:12.236
Thanks, but a surprise is good
every once in a while.

21:12.238 --> 21:13.271
Wouldn't you agree?

21:13.273 --> 21:14.438
Ah!

21:15.807 --> 21:19.010
( laughing )

21:21.413 --> 21:25.883
<i>♪ I think Earth</i>
<i>is a pretty gre-at place ♪</i>

21:25.885 --> 21:27.785
<i>♪ That's saying something</i>

21:27.787 --> 21:30.054
<i>♪ 'Cause I've been</i>
<i>through outer space ♪</i>

21:30.056 --> 21:33.924
<i>♪ I think it suits me,</i>
<i>it's just my style ♪</i>

21:33.926 --> 21:38.062
<i>♪ I think I'm gonna stay</i>
<i>a little while ♪</i>

21:38.064 --> 21:42.066
♪ I think that strangers are
just friends you haven't met ♪

21:42.068 --> 21:46.103
<i>♪ I'm blasting monsters</i>
<i>and I never break a sweat ♪</i>

21:46.105 --> 21:50.474
<i>♪ I'm really thinking</i>
<i>I could call this place home ♪</i>
